item.title: S2AND: Allen AI Paper Summary
item.description: Introduction The purpose of this post is to provide readers a quick recap on the S2AND paper by Allen AI. Readers are encouraged to review the original paper for technical details they wish to further investigate. Additionally, Daniel King and Sergey Feldman have done a great job documenting S2AND development in a separate Medium post by Sergey Feldman. For a post demonstrating the implementation of S2AND, feel free to read the second part of this post.
